      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked through, transfer it to to a clean board and shred apart using two forks, then set aside – this is your <strong>pulled chicken</strong></p><p>Decrease the heat to medium-high and cook the<strong> onion</strong> and <strong>mushrooms</strong> for a further 3-4 min or until caramelised</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
