        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained linguine</strong> and <strong>pulled chicken</strong> to the pan with the <strong>chicken stock</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until slightly thickened</p><p>Once thickened, remove the pan from the heat and add your <strong>crème fraîche</strong> – this is your <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>chicken thigh &</strong> <strong>mushroom stroganoff</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of the starchy pasta water if the sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
